usage: hyperopt_tune.py [-h] [--config-name CONFIG_NAME]
                        [--max-evals MAX_EVALS] [--tune-epochs TUNE_EPOCHS]
                        [--tune-patience TUNE_PATIENCE] [--log-wandb]
                        [--seed SEED] [--search-algo {tpe,random}]
                        [--space-yaml SPACE_YAML] [--run-group RUN_GROUP]
                        [--run-axis RUN_AXIS] [--run-phase RUN_PHASE]
                        [--parent-result PARENT_RESULT]

Hyperopt (TPE) hyperparameter tuning for RecBole models

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --config-name CONFIG_NAME
                        Hydra config name (e.g. tune_ml, tune_ab)
  --max-evals MAX_EVALS
                        Number of hyperopt trials (default: 50)
  --tune-epochs TUNE_EPOCHS
                        Override epoch count for tuning (default: use config
                        value)
  --tune-patience TUNE_PATIENCE
                        Override early-stopping patience (default: use config
                        value)
  --log-wandb           Enable wandb logging for this tuning session
  --seed SEED           Random seed for TPE sampler (default: 42)
  --search-algo {tpe,random}
                        Search algorithm for hyperopt fmin (default: tpe)
  --space-yaml SPACE_YAML
                        Optional YAML file with {fixed, search} to override
                        tuning space.
  --run-group RUN_GROUP
                        Run group label for result partitioning (e.g.
                        baseline, fmoe).
  --run-axis RUN_AXIS   Run axis label (e.g. train, hparam, layout, schedule).
  --run-phase RUN_PHASE
                        Optional pipeline phase label (e.g. P0, P1, ...).
  --parent-result PARENT_RESULT
                        Optional parent result JSON path.

Examples:
  python hyperopt_tune.py --config-name tune_ml model=sasrec gpu_id=0
  python hyperopt_tune.py --config-name tune_ab model=fame --max-evals 60
  python hyperopt_tune.py --config-name tune_rr model=gru4rec --tune-epochs 50
  python hyperopt_tune.py --config-name tune_ml model=sigma --log-wandb
